<abstract>Chloe Hooper attended Lauriston Girls' School before commencing a Bachelor of Arts at the University of Melbourne. She studied creative writing at New York's Columbia University under a Fulbright Scholarship.

Hooper's first novel <span style="font-style:italic">A Child's Book of True Crime</span> was launched at the 2002 Adelaide Writers' Week.</abstract>
